While patrolling North Ithilien, you have encountered an Olog-hai of Minas Morgul.

With no fear of the returned sunlight, this creature poses a grave threat to the Rangers of Ithilien as well as the Host of the West.

You should defeat the Olog-hai before your time in North Ithilien is at an end.
One of the last Olog-hai of Minas Morgul to survive the Battle of the Pelennor Fields, Ognir now wanders North Ithilien and crushes all in his path.
Warband: Ognir, Warrior of Minas Morgul
You have defeated the terrible Olog-hai, Ognir, and cleared a path for the Host of the West.\n\nThe Rangers of Ithilien are grateful for your efforts to secure North Ithilien.
You have defeated the Olog-hai, Ognir!
